      "id": "PopularPost9338",
      "post_content": "I love it when people call creatures, \"monsters.\"  \nI also love permanents that let you untap other permanents. They are grossly overpowered.  \n  \nTurn 3 [Wake Thrasher](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wake Thrasher)  \nTurn 4 [Filigree Sages](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Filigree Sages)  \nTurn 5 [Gilded Lotus](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gilded Lotus) (tap Lotus, untap with Sages, repeat...), into infinitely big Wake Thrasher.  \n  \nI'm sure he has a lot more interesting T2 uses.  ",
      "posted_by": "Kenji18",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost9338\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">I love it when people call creatures, \"monsters.\"<br/>I also love permanents that let you untap other permanents.  They are grossly overpowered.<br/><br/>Turn 3 <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Wake Thrasher\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wake Thrasher\">Wake Thrasher</a><br/>Turn 4 <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Filigree Sages\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Filigree Sages\">Filigree Sages</a><br/>Turn 5 <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Gilded Lotus\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gilded Lotus\">Gilded Lotus</a> (tap Lotus, untap with Sages, repeat...), into infinitely big Wake Thrasher.<br/><br/>I'm sure he has a lot more interesting T2 uses.<br/></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '9338'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy1819\">Kenji18</span>\r\n                                (6/19/2009 1:13:11 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_Sub