    {
      "id": "PopularPost165692",
      "post_content": "Never was impressed with this card, when I heard esper was coming out I hoped there would be a card comparable to [Clock of Omens](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Clock of Omens), [Dross Scorpion](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dross Scorpion), or even [Voltaic Construct](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Voltaic Construct) but I was sadly, sadly disappoint.  \n  \nNever underestimate the power of untap abilities that don't require coloured mana for their activation  \n  \nusually I would pick Voltaic Construct over this, as this is only useful with [training grounds](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=training grounds), Usually I don't have a problem with Voltaic Construct targeting non-creature artifacts as I usually have a [March of the Machines](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=March of the Machines ) out around turn 4.  \n  \nStill its not so bad as an untap ability to sink left over mana into is always useful during your oponents end step.",
      "posted_by": "Ava_Adore",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost165692\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">Never was impressed with this card, when I heard esper was coming out I hoped there would be a card comparable to <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Clock of Omens\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Clock of Omens\">Clock of Omens</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Dross Scorpion\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dross Scorpion\">Dross Scorpion</a>, or even <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Voltaic Construct\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Voltaic Construct\">Voltaic Construct</a> but I was sadly, sadly disappoint.<br/><br/>Never underestimate the power of untap abilities that don't require coloured mana for their activation<br/><br/>usually I would pick Voltaic Construct over this, as this is only useful with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"training grounds\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=training grounds\">training grounds</a>, Usually I don't have a problem with Voltaic Construct targeting non-creature artifacts as I usually have a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"March of the Machines \" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=March of the Machines \">March of the Machines </a>out around turn 4.<br/><br/>Still its not so bad as an untap ability to sink left over mana into is always useful during your oponents end step.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '165692'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00